  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A pixel-faithful mirror of the award-winning oryzo.ai homepage by Lusion — a real-time 3D Gaussian-splat product scene (a cork coaster on a cutting mat) with scroll-driven camera choreography, MSDF kinetic type, Rive animation, and product-gallery video. Renders in the sandboxed preview. Large media (the 3D splat, the Three.js bundle, and the Rive runtime) are served from the repository-assets CDN; one testimonial section embeds a Vimeo-hosted video. Everything else is bundled locally.",
  "description_i18n": {
    "en": "A pixel-faithful mirror of the award-winning oryzo.ai homepage by Lusion — a real-time 3D Gaussian-splat product scene (a cork coaster on a cutting mat) with scroll-driven camera choreography, MSDF kinetic type, Rive animation, and product-gallery video. Renders in the sandboxed preview. Large media (the 3D splat, the Three.js bundle, and the Rive runtime) are served from the repository-assets CDN; one testimonial section embeds a Vimeo-hosted video. Everything else is bundled locally.",
    "zh-CN": "Lusion 出品的获奖站点 oryzo.ai 主页的像素级镜像——实时 3D 高斯泼溅产品场景(切割垫上的软木杯垫），含滚动驱动的相机编排、MSDF 动态文字、Rive 动画和产品画廊视频。可在沙箱预览中渲染。大媒体（3D 泼溅、Three.js bundle、Rive 运行时）从 repository-assets CDN 提供；一个推荐区块嵌入 Vimeo 托管视频。其余全部本地打包。"
  },
